                            <comment id="13654980" author="tabish121" created="Fri, 10 May 2013 22:52:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;No test case for reproducing this.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14066320" author="dejanb" created="Fri, 18 Jul 2014 13:15:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is now fixed on the trunk. The root of the problem was that LevelDBStore was also a TransactionStore. So, when broker was stopping the TransactionBroker was stopping the whole store earlier than it should, leading to this error later in the process.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
